variables:
--1)static typed and dynamic type:
1)variables
2)variables are used to store the data(any kind of data)

variables:
1>case-sensitive
2>start with letters,(under_score),$(dollarsign)
3>can't start with numbers
4>Reserved works(keyword)not allowed
5>Allowed letters,_(under_score),$(dollarsign),numbers


How to declare variables:
> var
> let
> const

1)var keyword 1995-2015
2)let keyword 2015
3)var used only old browsers
-----------------------------
Example:1                    
     var a=1;                
       a=5;                 
       document.write(a+a)  
       console.log(a+a)      
o/p:10                       

--redeclaring with var is not accepted
--redeclaring with (let,const) is not accepted

Block scope:
variables declared with var does not have 
let allows the block scope
